WEBVTT

00:01.567 --> 00:04.069
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.103 --> 00:06.304
Boy, oh, boy,
oh, boy. Yep.

00:06.305 --> 00:08.239
Woody's wedding was quite
an event, wasn't it, Norm?

00:08.240 --> 00:09.740
Oh, man.
Huh, huh?

00:09.775 --> 00:11.842
Boy, what a night
that was. Yeah.

00:11.843 --> 00:13.060
Yeah, the priest dying.
Yeah.

00:13.061 --> 00:14.963
Carla being caught
in a dumb-waiter.

00:14.997 --> 00:16.297
Ha!

00:16.299 --> 00:18.032
How about that German guy
trying to kill Sam?

00:18.033 --> 00:19.000
(chuckling)

00:19.001 --> 00:20.134
"Du, dort!"

00:20.169 --> 00:22.103
Remember that?

00:22.137 --> 00:23.738
Yeah, oh, golly.

00:23.739 --> 00:25.407
Oh, yeah, but all that
was nothing

00:25.408 --> 00:26.824
compared to the
wedding itself. Yeah.

00:26.825 --> 00:29.143
Oh, now, there
was a comedy of errors.

00:29.178 --> 00:30.578
(chuckling)

00:30.613 --> 00:32.447
Hey, it's not
quite 2:00.

00:32.448 --> 00:34.749
What do you say we, uh,
stop off at Cheers, huh?

00:34.750 --> 00:36.518
Won't, uh...
won't Vera be angry?

00:36.552 --> 00:37.602
She'll never know.

00:37.603 --> 00:38.820
Yeah, well, I guess not.

00:38.821 --> 00:40.322
She... she sure
put away

00:40.323 --> 00:41.389
that champagne at the wedding.

00:41.390 --> 00:43.758
Yeah, she's a big girl.

00:43.793 --> 00:46.795
Yeah, she's still
out cold, too.

00:46.829 --> 00:48.396
(sighs)

00:48.431 --> 00:51.533
Okay, just don't slam the
door when you get out.

00:51.567 --> 00:53.435
And remember...
crack a window.

00:53.436 --> 00:55.203
You're a good husband,
Norm Peterson.

00:55.204 --> 00:58.540
(theme song begins)

01:00.542 --> 01:03.011
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:03.045 --> 01:06.647
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:08.550 --> 01:12.553
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:12.588 --> 01:15.289
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:15.324 --> 01:18.059
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:18.094 --> 01:22.030
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

